\title{First Sets in \deplambek}
\author{stevenschaefer}
\taxon{Definition}
\date{2025-01-24}

\tag{deplambek}

\import{grammar-macros}

\p{
  The [first set](sss-000Y) of a grammar #{A} may be captured in \deplambek via the following proposition:

  ##{ c \not \in \first{A} := A \And (\literal{c} \otimes \top) \vdash \bot}
}
